#  Microservices with Spring Boot – Hands-on

##  Project Overview

In this hands-on project, I created two microservices using Spring Boot:

- **Account Service**
- **Loan Service**

The objective of this exercise was to understand how microservices work and how they communicate with each other using REST APIs.

---

##  Technologies Used

- Java  
- Spring Boot  
- REST APIs  
- Maven  
- IntelliJ IDEA  

---

